metadata.name: Pondering
metadata.description:
This is 1 NFT in a collection of 6 photos each of which is unique and the only edition.  

4000x6000‬ px.

 What are the dangers of resonant, pseudo-philosophical thinking? 

Because many people consider their fruitless thought processes to be a useful action; they believe that they are really not wasting time, as there is large-scale brain activity going on.

But the absence of thought also cannot be called a healthy human condition.

Balance is important.
